<paragraph role="paragraph" id="par_id3149667" xml-lang="en-US" l10n="U" oldref="6">You can move selected objects in your slide by dragging them, using the arrow keys, or by copying the objects and pasting them in another location.</paragraph>
<list type="unordered">
<listitem>
<paragraph role="listitem" id="par_id3145799" xml-lang="en-US" l10n="U" oldref="7">The arrow keys let you move objects more precisely than with the mouse.<comment>UFI: add grid, guides, snap points</comment></paragraph>
</listitem>
